SQL_STMT_U.val: select FM09.FM09_ADMNO, FM09.FM09_CLNTNO, FM09.FM09_NO, FM09.FM09_SCHT_NO from :1/FM09 FM09, :1/SCHT SCHT where FM09.FM09_SCHT_NO = SCHT.SCHT_NO and SCHT.SCHT_SCHEDDATERECV <= ':2' and SCHT.SCHT_BOOKED = 'Y' and FM09.FM09_SCHT_NO > 0 and FM09.FM09_FM17_NO = 0 order by FM09.FM09_ADMNO, FM09.FM09_CLNTNO for fetch only

Text.val: Only if V.COMMISSIONC > 0 then continue with the next steps, else continue with
the next client
set FCMH_REPA_JOURNALNO = PO.JOURNALNO
5. Charge the client for the commission
type = 152
type = 87
V.COMMISSION_HANDLINGC <> 0
V.COMMISSION_INSURANCEC <> 0

SQL_STMT_U.val: select cast (sum (FI09_COMMISSION) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (FI09_COMMISSION_HANDLING) as decimal (13,2)), cast (sum (FI09_COMMISSION_INSURANCE) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/FI09 where FI09_FM09_NO = :2 for fetch only

select FM09.FM09_ADMNO, FM09.FM09_CLNTNO, FM09.FM09_NO, FM09.FM09_SCHT_NO from :1/FM09 FM09, :1/SCHT SCHT where FM09.FM09_SCHT_NO = SCHT.SCHT_NO and SCHT.SCHT_SCHEDDATERECV <= ':2' and SCHT.SCHT_BOOKED = 'Y' and FM09.FM09_SCHT_NO > 0 and FM09.FM09_FM17_NO = 0 and FM09.FM09_ADMNO = :3 and FM09.FM09_CLNTNO = :4 order by FM09.FM09_ADMNO, FM09.FM09_CLNTNO for fetch only
select FI09.FI09_DOCNR, FI09.FI09_BUYER_NO from :1/FI09 FI09, :1/FM09 FM09 where FI09.FI09_FM09_NO = FM09.FM09_NO and FI09.FI09_FM09_NO = :2 and FI09.FI09_COMMISSION <> 0 for fetch only
